{"tid":1783211,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【怪錯G.E.M.了?】G.E.M.新歌暗寸中國腐敗 網民等睇變禁歌","createTime":"2019-12-14T15:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T00:27:53.000Z","uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fa3075506e4acb4bbe2b180d6cae67e3fde3ed","tid":1783211,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191214/large/1576306797_8251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576306797_8251.jpg&h=0443f629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宇宙級歌手G.E.M.鄧紫棋自從在中國參加「真人騷」節目《我是歌手》於中國爆紅後，一直將工作重心放在中國。今年3月G.E.M.突然與提攜她出道的蜂鳥音樂結束11年的合作關係，成立「鄧紫棋工作室」繼續專注於中國發展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191214/large/1576306797_b78c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576306797_b78c.jpg&h=9e37ab21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿G.E.M.新MV出現疑似揶揄中國的畫面及歌詞（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n昨日G.E.M.推出的新歌《摩天動物園》惹來網民熱烈討論，事關這首由阿G.E.M.親自作曲填詞的作品，當中出現大量中國敏感字眼，當中一段歌詞「當鼻子愛上了霧霾 一開始察覺不出來 這一種腐敗 它像骨牌 慢慢地覆蓋 把你毒害」更疑似直指中國北京政府的現況，加上MV當中又穿插大量「人形豬」、「活摘器官」等敏感場面，有網民笑指成為「禁歌」指日可待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191214/large/1576306798_3ad7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576306798_3ad7.jpg&h=f177c5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n包括紅色天空底下的「人形豬」（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n而歌詞當中的一段「於是學着蟑螂 到處爬着牆 不怕黑也不怕髒 大便也舔上 為了要前往 光鮮的監房」爭議最大，有網民認為該段歌詞是在嘲笑理大手足，亦有人認為按上文下理解讀的話是在嘲諷向權力諂媚的人，最終被關進牢獄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191214/large/1576306797_c6fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576306797_c6fb.jpg&h=c64185a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n活摘器官（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n其實撇開可能存在的政治隱喻及立場，阿G.E.M.新歌當中有不少歌詞直指現今中國社會風氣的扭曲及腐敗，如「穿灰衣的姑娘得不到尊重 社會大眾不在乎微小昆蟲 於是一群羔羊卑微的願望 是努力擠進荒涼 庸俗的天堂」、「你和我生來都是曾經白的紙 只是同樣被寫上太多歪的字」、「單純的一群小白豬 被名和利薰陶擺佈 衣服都故意少塊布 淪為了潮牌奴 賣了靈魂撈財富」等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191214/large/1576306800_9a27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576306800_9a27.jpg&h=b24d4a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191214/60377498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191214%2F60377498&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=e2c9ba48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191214%2F60377498&h=f70d09e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191214/60377498</a>"},{"pid":"7206841f5b124faa40608a38092380df4668fb60","tid":1783211,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"937dfbfb8cb6c687d221a95ebb9d839050088ea2","tid":1783211,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會係F F得太多"},{"pid":"16adf640f142312d678dd8b5aaaae9100141858d","tid":1783211,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"搵大陸搵錢最紅個幾個<br />\n無一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"5e2abdabf9d8fc1c42dfd4600c14e3775b87ad9b","tid":1783211,"uid":335189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"當然 「唔係 都推到佢係 」 ！"},{"pid":"5b44c7421e6a116ceecd3dc4e3be737e9b775fb7","tid":1783211,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e2abdabf9d8fc1c42dfd4600c14e3775b87ad9b","tid":1783211,"uid":335189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"當然 「唔係 都推到佢係 」 ！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633c919575df082279a14acae27d893eb3efcf53","tid":1783211,"uid":262539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T00:27:53.000Z","msg":"其實香港唔可以自high<br />\n要有人輸出教育先得"}]}